	var upcomingDates = [
		{type:"Classroom", id:65, title:"Xactimate 28 Regional Training", ls:589},
		{type:"Virtual", id:444, title:"Xactimate 28 Virtual Classroom Training", ls:690}
	];
	var r = Math.floor(Math.random() * upcomingDates.length);
	var upcomingDate = upcomingDates[r];
	$.getJSON("//www.xactware.com/store/TrainingDatesInfo.do?callback=?", {courseIds: upcomingDate.id}, function (data){
		var today = new Date().getTime();
		var counter = 0;
		var utDiv = $("<div />").addClass("upcoming-training-container");
		$.each(data, function(key, info){
			var startPieces = info.start.split(' ');
			var startDate = startPieces[0];
			if (new Date(startDate) < today) return;
			if (counter++ == 3) return false;
			var endPieces = info.end.split(' ');
			var endDate = endPieces[0];
			var startTime = startPieces[1] + " " + startPieces[2];
			var endTime = endPieces[1] + " " + endPieces[2];
			var linkDescription;
			var additionalDescription;
			if (upcomingDate.type==="Classroom") {
				linkDescription = info.city+", "+info.state;
				additionalDescription = startDate+" - "+endDate;
			} else if (upcomingDate.type==="Virtual") {
				if (startDate != endDate) {
					linkDescription = startDate+" - "+endDate;
				} else {
					linkDescription = startDate;
				}
				additionalDescription = startTime + " - " + endTime;
			}
			utDiv.append($("<a href='http://www.xactware.com/store/SelectProd.do?prodId="+upcomingDate.id+"&amp;SFCID=70130000000WxB2&amp;LS="+upcomingDate.ls+"'></a>").addClass("location").text(linkDescription));
			utDiv.append($("<span />").addClass("dates").text(additionalDescription));
		});
		$('.upcoming-trainings').append(utDiv).append('<p>'+upcomingDate.title+'</p>');
	});
// ]]>
